  "description": [
    "Mayors To Meet In Dover Sunday Civil defense will be the chief subject at a meeting of the Dela ware Mayors Association to be held in Legislative Hall Dover at 2 p m this coming Saturday with the civil defense coordinators of all communities of the state being asked to meet with the members of the association for the discus sion Mayor William J Storey Dover president of the association has been advised by Major D Preston Lee Wilmington state civil de fense coordinator that Michael P Rooney regional civil defense di rector of the area comprising Del aware Pennsylvania Maryland and Virginia will be present with Mayor Lee at the meeting Plans Announced In letters to members announc ing plans for the meeting Dover City Manager 0B Agner associ ation secretary explains The president of the associe tion thinks it is highly advisable that all of the local civil defense coor dinators be present It is common knowledge that our civil defense is lagging and the opinion of all concerned is that this is a highly desirable activity and should be encouraged The association has associated with it 63 mayors city managers gnd town council presidents J Wallace Woodford"
  ],
